room_title: Escape room "A Christmas Story Escape" by Escape Room Center in Bridgewater
room_description: Can you help Ralphie get his dream Christmas present: a Red Ryder Carbine Action 200-shot Range Model air rifle?  Based on Jean Shepherd's famous holiday story which was turned into one of the funniest Christmas movies of all time, this escape room contains family-friendly fun for die-hard fans as well as those not familiar with the story.
